                                            SUBWAY ENVIRONMENT SIMULATION
                                                  SIMULATION OF
                         SES v4.1 file with a simple rail tunnel (up line, down line, one station).
                         Explicit train speed, implicit performance calculation.
                         Uses all forms except form 4 (fires), 6C to 6H (use the ECZs run for those),
                         8D (dwell locations), 9J (decel rates), 9K and 9L (flywheels) and 10
                         (initial trains).
                         Humidity displayed as kg/kg of dry air.
                         This file does not correctly calculate the tractive/braking effort needed to
                         go up and down hills due to the bug in Train.for (see section 5 of the Notes).
                         Supplementary print option set to 0 (designer-only stuff).
                         This file has some oddities included to prove that the plots are working,
                         such as non-fire segments in the running tunnels, reversed sections,
                         jet fans and train types with odd train performance properties.
                         Do not use it as a basis for other files unless you need the weird.
                         If the runtime is extended to 1810 seconds, an ECZ estimate occurs that raises
                         simulation error 8 (failed ECZ estimate).
                                    DESIGN TIME 1700 HRS   JULY       2029
                                                                                             DEVELOPED BY -
                                                                                               PARSONS, BRINCKERHOFF,
                                                                                               QUADE AND DOUGLAS, INC.
                                                                                               NEW YORK CITY, NEW YORK
